171 A.3d 1261 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DENNIS AIELLO, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-227 Sept.Term 2017

079468 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004514-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
